Convoy landed hard smiling as he watched her fly overhead. "Have a 
nice flight." He stood and walked over to Kup. "Thank you for the 
back-up my friend, I hope one day I can repay the favor." He turned 
and walked over to windlord and Rave. 

Rave looked up at WindLord... "Oh brother... Remind me to avoid her 
next battle..." He looked down seeing his exposed 
ribcage... "Ouch..." He lay back blacking out again...

Sabre landed and surveyed the others... Wheeljack-x, kup, and 
windlord... Allies... Wingrazor alive but damaged, convoy attending 
to rave... He quickly went to WingRazor's side... "Wing?"

The eagles eyes were closed tight both wings were mangled from the 
crash, while her back was burnt and featherless her nano drive was 
working as fuzzy down feathers began growing...
**************

NightViper hissed. "Noo, take the bassse, we will not surrender, 
glory to the Pre...." He went slack blacking out as his reptle flesh 
hung lose and torn his hood was in tatters as his eyes dimmed...
